  "_notes": [
    "Panels, distribution boards, switchgear, junction boxes, isolators.",
    "Connector-bearing \u2014 supports auto-routing termination + the panel-",
    "schedule pipeline (ELC_PNL_*). Standalone hosting since panels are",
    "typically wall-mounted but the family ships unhosted so it can be",
    "placed in plant rooms / on Reference Lines / against work planes.",
    "",
    "16 type variants covering: consumer units (6/12/18W), distribution",
    "boards (3-phase), main switchboards, isolators, MCCs, UPS, VFDs,",
    "soft starters, busbar trunking, ATS, RCD units."
