      "_connector_notes": [
        "Two power (Domain='Electrical') connectors for circuiting stay as-is per",
        "the domain contract \u2014 a panel/DB is fed and loaded by power connectors, not",
        "conduit. systemType='Power' -> ElectricalSystemType.PowerCircuit (was absent",
        "before -> UndefinedSystemType, which CreateElectricalConnector rejects). Old",
        "x/y/z/direction keys did NOT bind (creator reads offsetX/offsetY/offsetZ +",
        "facing), so both collapsed to (0,0,0) facing -X; fixed to real box faces.",
        "A third Domain='Conduit' terminal is ADDED so a panel also becomes a conduit",
        "auto-route anchor: AutoConduitDrop.FindBestFreeConnector() bonds a rising",
        "conduit from this stub to the nearest containment, matching the junction-box",
        "and fixture seeds. Offset in X keeps it clear of the top load connector."
      ],
